title: MLA Ravi Rana, wife MP Navneet decide to recite Hanuman Chalisa in front of Matoshri, served notice - India Today
content: MLA Ravi Rana, wife MP Navneet decide to recite Hanuman Chalisa in front of Matoshri, served notice  India TodayView Full coverage on Google News
description: Maharashtra MP Navneet Rana and her husband MLA Ravi Rana have said that they would recite the Hanuman Chalisa in front of Matoshri, the residence of CM Udhav Thackeray.
